=================================================

Lowly council employee Sam Pinkett is the sole witness to a shocking car accident. 

Answering a ringing mobile phone which he finds at the crash site, he suddenly finds himself mixed up in a deadly kidnap plot. 

Shocked and hungover, Sam also has problems mounting up at work, where his boss and ex-girlfriend Lizzie feels like he isn't pulling his weight. But his excitable colleague Phil convinces him they need to step up and save the day.
 
 
 



1/6 A case of mistaken identity catapults two council employees into a conspiracy.

2/6 Sam and Phil are sent to rescue a hostage, but end up with an angry hostage of their own.

3/6 Sam and Phil fall deeper into a sinister world of agents and double agents.

4/6 Sam and Phil gatecrash a party, inadvertently interrupting an assassination plot.

5/6 Sam and Phil bring the dangerous plot right to their doorsteps and nowhere is safe

6/6 Sam and Phil are now on the run, on the edge and on each other's nerves.
